📖 How to Use This Library

This repository is organized by chapter modules. Each folder contains:

01-Summaries & 02-Study Guides: Core concepts and mechanical derivations.

03-Infographics: Visual intuition maps for comparing linear and rotational analogs.

04-Worksheets: Practice sets for problem-solving mastery.

05-SmartSheets: Interactive HTML tools for rapid calculation and parameter testing.

06-Simulations: Numerical engines (RK4/Semi-Implicit Euler) featuring Triple-View diagnostics (Time-Domain, Phase Space, and Energy charts).

07-Media: Curated video demonstrations and lecture links.

